{"tid":1676260,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今次譚仔事件睇到，港共就係得呢一招","createTime":"2019-10-26T10:34:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T14:33:04.000Z","uid":166785,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"73a14dec4f61e0bb0c038adeff31ab497da95771","tid":1676260,"uid":166785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T10:34:36.000Z","msg":"港共學足中共果套，分化，借刀殺人，拉一個打一個，由雨傘到而家都係咁，我唔係叫大家唔好裝修，但真係諗清楚，睇定立場先好去做，一黎就18區一齊黎清佢場<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算錯左，屌完都不割，記住兄弟爬山各自努力"},{"pid":"a1dd1183468d0a45aaedcac64929b6db6c358e34","tid":1676260,"uid":166785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T10:36:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a24ad53b8d4a01662572be0b9428bbc0a3362f51","tid":1676260,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T10:46:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ftNY3bs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FftNY3bs.jpg&h=52c3e770&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n討論完譚仔未 使唔使幾百個post呀<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日尖沙咀見！</span></span>"},{"pid":"05b305ff73c6d58b8b9b03ccbf6e1c23017b1749","tid":1676260,"uid":242647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a24ad53b8d4a01662572be0b9428bbc0a3362f51","tid":1676260,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T10:46:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ftNY3bs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FftNY3bs.jpg&h=52c3e770&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n討論完譚仔未 使唔使幾百個post呀<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"fo